title: I Kissed a Succubus
description:
That kiss is for the sake of survival... Or is it?
Yukiko is a normal junior high school girl, living a peaceful life with her childhood friend, Fuu.
However, her peace is shattered by a sudden kiss from transfer student Konomi.
Konomi is a succubus who is trying to get Yukiko's life energy, but Yukiko has a secret of her own.
author: Mochi Shiratama

06.title: We Are the Cute Succubus Sisters
